  m_Text: Plug in a controller, as the two-player mode does not function with the
    keyboard. Make sure that the controller is a PS3 or PS4, otherwise the game will
    break. The controller must have an operating tempreture of 600 to 1000000 degrees.
    Using the controller at during summer will shut down the controller forever. Please
    make sure that you contact 312-329-1fwefww for assistance.
